name: 1,3,7-trimethylnaphthalene

But the overall effect of methyl groups on a polycyclic aromatic compound tends to decrease the melting point due to steric hindrance and reduced planarity. Prediction: 80 (naphthalene) - 25 (methyl group effect x 3 methyl groups) = 5 degrees Celsius
